            </svg>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 hidden group-hover:block shadow rounded-3xl bg-black text-white p-5 pl-10 w-[30vw]">
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>Frontend development using Nuxt/Vue frameworks and Typescript</li>
                <br>
                <li>Backend development with Node/Express.js</li>
                <br>
                <li>Implemented custom image rendering on the Backend for downloads</li>
                <br>
                <li>Integration of APIs of several video-games: Fortnite, Counter-Strike, League of Legends</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-row h-36 w-[25vw]">
        <img src="/assets/xtremeai.png" alt="xtremeai" class="w-36 rounded-3xl mr-4 object-contain">
        <div class="flex flex-col relative flex-grow">
          <p class="font-bold">Xtreme.ai</p>
          <p>November 2020 - April 2021</p>
          <p>Software Engineering Internship</p>
