              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>Front-end development of a platform for Glovo, used in digitalizing restaurant menus and serving to Glovo API endpoints</li>
                <br>
                <li>FullStack development (Vue.js/Django) of tool for digitalizing restaurant menus utilizing recognition of text from images (OCR/OpenCV)</li>
                <br>
                <li>Integration and evaluation of metrics composed with Python (Pandas, Keras, PyTorch) and served to be visualized in Metabase</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-row h-36 w-[25vw]">
        <img src="/assets/mubint.svg" alt="mubint" class="w-36 mr-4 object-contain">
